<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA18">
<l>vāymoḻintu vāmaṉaṉāy māvalipāṉ mūvaṭima</l>
<l>ṇīyaḷantu koṇṭa neṭumālē – tāviyaniṉ</l>
<l>ṉeñcā viṇaiyaṭikkē yēḻpiṟappu māḷāki</l>
<l>yañcā tirukka varuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O tall Māl, you who speaking truth as a dwarf, measured</l>
<l>[and] took the earth from Māvali with three steps,</l>
<l>bless [me] with being without fear as a servant</l>
<l>through all seven births to your undiminishing two feet that leapt [over the worlds].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
